    <briefdescription>
<para>System that resets the hasUpdate flag on all MaxScoreObserverComponents. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Scheduled after the UI binding systems have consumed the update. This ensures that MaxScoreObserverComponent::hasUpdate() returns true for exactly one frame after a high score change.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1scoring_1_1systems_1_1MaxScoreObserverSystem" kindref="compound">MaxScoreObserverSystem</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>MaxScoreObserverComponent </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
